’Щ@0fde7033b37b94a2671f2807ce5e26b7295452821962f6b71aaa612a36b29843Ъ	Title: title: str distance
Path: Examples
Content:
Get the edit distance between two strings.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 'nushell' | str distance 'nutshell'
1

```
Compute edit distance between strings in table and another string, using cell paths.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [{a: 'nutshell' b: 'numetal'}] | str distance 'nushell' 'a' 'b'
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ a в”Ӯ b в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 0 в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Compute edit distance between strings in record and another string, using cell paths.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> {a: 'nutshell' b: 'numetal'} | str distance 'nushell' a b
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ a в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ b в”Ӯ 4 в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ

```
